    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Dust-laden whirlwinds that move across arid regions. They are generally associated with hot, dry air, and electrical tension. </Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
